text: 20th Corps, Twentieth Corps, or XX Corps may refer to: * XX Corps (German Empire) * XX Corps (Ottoman Empire) * XX Corps (United Kingdom) * XX Corps (United States) * XX Corps (Union Army), a unit in the American Civil War * XX Army Corps (Wehrmacht) * XX Motorised Corps (Italy) * 20th Army Corps (Russian Empire) ==See also== * List of military corps by number * 20th Army (disambiguation) * 20th Brigade (disambiguation) * 20th Division (disambiguation) * 20th Regiment (disambiguation) * 20 Squadron (disambiguation)
